      },
      {
        "type": "regex",
        "pattern": "https?://[a-zA-Z0-9._-]+:[^@\\s'\"<>`{}]{8,100}@[a-zA-Z0-9._-]+(?::[0-9]{1,5})?(?:/[^\\s]*)?",
        "message": "Ping Identity HTTP/HTTPS URL with embedded admin credentials detected. PingFederate, PingAccess, and PingOne admin consoles use web-based authentication. These credentials provide full administrative access to identity services including SSO configuration, API gateway policies, user federation, and access control. Exposure enables identity theft, unauthorized access to protected resources, privilege escalation, and compromise of integrated applications. Revoke exposed credentials immediately and use secure authentication methods.",
