        "type": "regex",
        "pattern": "(?<!://)\\b[a-zA-Z0-9._-]{3,50}:[^@\\s'\"<>`{}:/]{8,100}\\b",
        "message": "Ping Identity admin credentials in username:password format detected. These credentials are used for administrative access to Ping Identity platforms including PingFederate, PingAccess, PingDirectory, and PingOne. Hardcoded admin credentials provide complete control over identity and access management infrastructure. This enables attackers to modify user identities, bypass authentication, escalate privileges, access sensitive data, and compromise all integrated systems. Immediately rotate credentials, implement secrets management, and audit all administrative access.",
